Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.31,0:01:38.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 摇摆摇摆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.96,0:01:44.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一直游行到银河的尽头吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.83,0:01:47.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么?这艘太空船里有劫机客?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.70,0:01:50.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的，因此请你们把犯人抓起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.77,0:01:52.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.11,0:01:54.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我们的假期怎么办?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.78,0:01:59.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难得我用便宜价钱弄到手的渡假行星旅游机票
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.48,0:02:00.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的很可惜啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.58,0:02:04.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你一开始就知情了对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.29,0:02:06.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,关於这个犯人的资料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.62,0:02:08.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-姓名是艾克塞尔·西欧雷\N-喂，你早就知道了吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.49,0:02:09.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-性别是男性\N-是故意瞒我们的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.72,0:02:13.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-身高170公分，体重50公斤\N-喂，胡子，胡子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.23,0:02:14.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看来身材蛮修长的 真是叫人羡慕…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.10,0:02:16.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回去之後马上刮你的胡子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.17,0:02:19.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行，唯有胡子不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.39,0:02:24.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,#21嗨！吻仔鱼乾劫机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.94,0:02:27.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可恶，居然被设计了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.44,0:02:31.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,总之，事到如今只好快点找出犯人才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.38,0:02:33.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是要怎么找呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.41,0:02:36.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们穿这样太引人注意了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.72,0:02:38.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说的也是耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.59,0:02:40.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们明明有五个人居然那么没用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.26,0:02:43.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅琳少校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.69,0:02:45.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佯装成空姐就能解决了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.83,0:02:47.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这么简单的事难道你们想不到吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.90,0:02:50.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原来少校也搭乘这艘太空船啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.73,0:02:52.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是巧合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.10,0:02:56.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为华克中校给了我一张渡假行星的旅游机票
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.24,0:02:58.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原来如此，空姐啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.11,0:03:00.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.58,0:03:01.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.14,0:03:04.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在干什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.91,0:03:07.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当然是为了想假扮成空姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.32,0:03:09.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那你袭击她干嘛?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.18,0:03:12.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哎呀，原来是这样啊\N梅琳少校也被中校．．
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.65,0:03:13.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.89,0:03:17.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这表示中校根本不信任你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.89,0:03:19.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好意思，请给我一杯水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.30,0:03:21.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.23,0:03:22.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兰花拳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.37,0:03:28.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好险，我们的身分差点被揭穿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.37,0:03:30.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走开走开，没什么好看的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.77,0:03:32.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了，身分没有被揭穿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.97,0:03:35.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对啊，真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.44,0:03:36.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.28,0:03:44.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,身高170公分，身材削瘦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.12,0:03:47.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么样?有没有犯人的踪迹?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.96,0:03:49.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.12,0:03:53.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家都坐在位子上根本看不出身高差异
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.00,0:03:55.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是伤脑筋啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.50,0:03:56.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.63,0:03:59.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就叫大家站起来不就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.39,0:04:01.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么做?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.74,0:04:02.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦，就是这个，梅尔优
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.74,0:04:04.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是这个啦，梅尔优
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.11,0:04:08.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很好，你们都是乖孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.81,0:04:11.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要大吵大闹不然她真的会开枪喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.61,0:04:14.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个．．．兰花，能不能过来一下?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.98,0:04:17.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我现在很忙，等一下好吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.52,0:04:19.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么可以让你等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.32,0:04:23.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们是笨蛋吧，是笨蛋对吧没错，\N你们是笨蛋，笨蛋．．．
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.19,0:04:26.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜托，现在乱成一团\N你带那个恶心的家伙来干嘛?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.79,0:04:31.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为这个人身高170公分，体重50公斤啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.43,0:04:32.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的假的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.43,0:04:35.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅尔优，你立下大功了这家伙一定是犯人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.87,0:04:38.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错，怎么看都像犯人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.11,0:04:40.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位，请等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.91,0:04:42.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香草找到的这个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.71,0:04:45.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,身高体重也跟中校的资料一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.68,0:04:46.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这该怎么办?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.20,0:04:48.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯，这个嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.88,0:04:52.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太麻烦了，把两个人都当成犯人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.19,0:04:54.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在胡说八道什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.42,0:04:56.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那要怎么认定犯人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.56,0:04:59.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们手上的情报也只有身高体重啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.56,0:05:01.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么了?兰花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.66,0:05:05.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我刚刚想到一个超棒的好办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.53,0:05:08.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让他们两个上擂台比摔角怎么样?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.80,0:05:10.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一点创意都没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.10,0:05:12.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这算什么好办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.12,0:05:15.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么可以用比赛输赢来决定犯人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.24,0:05:16.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.38,0:05:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么没问题?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.58,0:05:19.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我早料到会有这种事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.18,0:05:23.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个布拉曼修财团秘密开发的虚拟游戏机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.28,0:05:24.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或许派得上用场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.45,0:05:27.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦，这是那个吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.27,0:05:31.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能在虚拟空间体验战斗的游戏机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.97,0:05:35.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我小时候在漫画里看过这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.13,0:05:37.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才不是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.73,0:05:41.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为就算让两个没有战斗意愿的人打斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.54,0:05:43.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根本得不到任何答案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.94,0:05:50.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以乾脆让他们受极刑，逼他们自己招供比较快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.51,0:05:52.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这和模拟游戏无关嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.11,0:05:54.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这根本是旁门左道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.87,0:05:56.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，那么大家一起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.95,0:05:59.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,闷绝闷绝，地狱攻击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.82,0:06:02.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇，两个人马上就招了耶\N(我是犯人)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.86,0:06:05.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不那么说的话铁定会被杀死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.83,0:06:09.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行啦，这种畜牲家伙说的话根本不能相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.20,0:06:12.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你比畜牲还要低级
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.60,0:06:15.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事件顺利解决太好了，太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.90,0:06:17.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.81,0:06:19.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么事件解决了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.81,0:06:23.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们连调查都没做不要随便定别人的罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.24,0:06:24.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请问
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.17,0:06:28.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从刚才一直没有看到香草
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.52,0:06:30.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她到哪里去了呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.32,0:06:32.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对喔，她到哪里去了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.82,0:06:37.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香草该不会被劫机犯抓去当人质了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.69,0:06:38.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不会吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.31,0:06:40.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你真的很莫名其妙耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.86,0:06:43.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,刚才你还说他们两个是犯人不是吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.83,0:06:45.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.27,0:06:48.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你这是干嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.80,0:06:52.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香草是我们重要的伙伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.44,0:06:53.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这我知道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.94,0:06:57.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我们要尽快把她从犯人的魔掌里救出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.95,0:07:00.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劫机嫌疑犯就在这里啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.48,0:07:02.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你懂不懂啊!地球有危险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.98,0:07:05.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦?什么危险?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.91,0:07:07.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位旅客请注意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.36,0:07:11.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在本机被神秘集团劫机了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.63,0:07:12.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我猜得果然没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.65,0:07:13.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.76,0:07:16.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在哪里?她一定是在说我们啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.69,0:07:19.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,总之，分头去找香草
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.53,0:07:22.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下，这些恶心的人怎么办?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.42,0:07:24.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香草
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.11,0:07:25.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香草，你在哪里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.31,0:07:27.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在哪里?香草
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.80,0:07:30.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的，快点出来啦，香草
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.98,0:07:33.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为发生了这些事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.45,0:07:36.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.78,0:07:40.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂，我查了一下身份背景\N这两个人根本不是什么犯人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.27,0:07:43.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哎呀，真是可惜啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.19,0:07:44.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们有找到吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.76,0:07:45.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.96,0:07:48.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到处都找不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.20,0:07:49.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.26,0:07:51.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香草那家伙到底跑到哪里去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.73,0:07:55.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在这里干什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.14,0:07:58.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哎呀，佛特，因为这里没人坐所以不小心就．．．
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.61,0:08:01.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不小心你个头啦\N你怎么可以坐在客人座位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.44,0:08:03.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好不容易装扮成空姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.11,0:08:06.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,万一我们的身份被其他旅客拆穿怎么办?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.78,0:08:10.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我跟你说，事到如今被拆穿还比较轻松
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.72,0:08:12.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大姊姊，这个位子有人坐喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.32,0:08:15.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,坐在这个位子的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.94,0:08:17.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从飞机起飞後就不晓得到哪里去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.64,0:08:19.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,直没有回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.83,0:08:20.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你说什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.83,0:08:23.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难道说，这个位子的人就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.17,0:08:25.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.50,0:08:30.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.97,0:08:33.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这位乘客提出的个人资料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.81,0:08:35.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完全查不到相关佐证
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.84,0:08:37.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这么说来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.25,0:08:42.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,应该没错他就是艾克塞尔·西欧雷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.82,0:08:47.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兰花，这艘太空船里还有哪里没找过的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.66,0:08:52.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只剩下船外和驾驶舱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.98,0:08:53.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.67,0:08:57.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香草，等著啊  我马上来救你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.30,0:08:59.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香草，你平安无事吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.63,0:09:00.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是什么人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.84,0:09:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你害人家担心死了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.41,0:09:07.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香草根本不需要你担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.58,0:09:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让我抱抱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.14,0:09:11.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了，找到香草了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.41,0:09:14.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊，劫机犯也顺利逮捕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.32,0:09:17.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜托，这个．．．他不是犯人，应该是机长吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.79,0:09:18.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,答对了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.75,0:09:23.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香草跟我只是来参观驾驶舱而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.95,0:09:24.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看，你们几个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.56,0:09:26.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,听到那只狸猫小鬼说的话了吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.79,0:09:28.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你才是老太婆咧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.20,0:09:29.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香草，是这样吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.43,0:09:32.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,搞什么，原来是这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.39,0:09:34.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一点都不好笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.54,0:09:37.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这下我们越来越像犯人了不是吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.67,0:09:40.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,总觉得这下真的惨了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.27,0:09:40.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.47,0:09:44.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个叫艾克塞尔的劫机犯也不在这里耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.61,0:09:47.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这都要怪你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.85,0:09:49.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,闭嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.62,0:09:52.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你干嘛突然打我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.91,0:09:55.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谜底终於全部揭晓了艾克塞尔·西欧雷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.28,0:09:57.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦?我?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.49,0:10:00.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是你在背後操控佛特的思考
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.19,0:10:04.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让我们天使队为你背负劫机犯的罪名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.77,0:10:06.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是高招啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.10,0:10:09.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错，难怪梅琳少校举止有点怪怪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.90,0:10:11.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这还不都是你们害的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.94,0:10:16.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且艾克塞尔是个男人为什么我这个女人．．．
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.98,0:10:18.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艾克塞尔是男的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.51,0:10:20.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要看我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.68,0:10:23.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我以前就觉得很可疑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.35,0:10:26.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,的确，这个人最近越来越男性化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.49,0:10:27.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,错不了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.27,0:10:30.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们根本错误连篇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.29,0:10:32.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那请你证明给我们看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.53,0:10:35.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请你让我们看看你是佛特·修特伦的证据
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.83,0:10:37.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好啊，就让你们看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.37,0:10:39.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,证明我是佛特而且是女人的证据
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.14,0:10:43.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你还没睡啊，哲郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.80,0:10:45.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是的，妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.17,0:10:47.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,该怎么说呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.51,0:10:50.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被逼看到不想看的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.38,0:10:52.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就这样无厘头闹下去的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.42,0:10:58.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然最後没有找到艾克塞尔·西欧雷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.45,0:11:00.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过，看来可以平安抵达目的地了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.59,0:11:01.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.32,0:11:04.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要结局是好的一切就0K
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.33,0:11:05.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什么关系呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.20,0:11:10.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天使 Rock'n'Roll
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.70,0:11:12.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老套的乐园
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.97,0:11:13.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊摇摆摇摆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.40,0:11:20.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,旋转的宇宙也在跳舞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.14,0:11:21.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是清白的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.81,0:11:23.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劫机犯是艾克塞尔·西欧雷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.88,0:11:25.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然抓不到艾克塞尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.52,0:11:29.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从整起事件的过程来看你们怎么看都像犯人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.68,0:11:32.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的渡假行星我向往的海滩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.92,0:11:35.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全都是你害的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.16,0:11:37.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可恶，给我记住艾克塞尔·西欧雷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.66,0:11:40.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个时候艾克塞尔·西欧雷呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.90,0:11:44.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(可恶!给我记住!银河天使!)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.53,0:11:47.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,猜拳十三奥义
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.33,0:11:49.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,开始罗，剪刀石头布
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.67,0:11:50.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,黄昏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.44,0:11:54.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,黄昏会令人感到悲伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.14,0:11:55.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,应该可以流泪吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.15,0:11:59.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雨下个不停?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.51,0:12:04.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊，都兰行星这一年来听说雨一直下个不停
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.92,0:12:06.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是乱来的异常气象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.79,0:12:08.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且惊人的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.12,0:12:11.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,整个星球的平衡依然正常维持著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.46,0:12:14.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有雨没完没了的下著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.80,0:12:16.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个也就是说．
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.23,0:12:19.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,八成是遗失文明造成的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.27,0:12:29.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,#22蓝色忧郁雨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.15,0:12:34.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其实都兰军附属的这个研究机构
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.54,0:12:37.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也得到了相同的结论
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.89,0:12:39.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因此才麻烦遗失文明的专家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.95,0:12:43.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是你们天使队来这里帮忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.62,0:12:45.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,专家是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.10,0:12:51.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,总之首先要让你们看个东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.77,0:12:53.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟我来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.55,0:13:12.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好可爱的女生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.29,0:13:13.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个女生是谁?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.95,0:13:17.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一年前战争的时候在保护机构遇见的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.76,0:13:19.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,战争孤儿啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.56,0:13:23.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你说要让我们看的就是这个女孩吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.13,0:13:26.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，不是这个女孩你们看得见吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.87,0:13:30.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这孩子胸部上的宝石
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.10,0:13:32.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难道那就是遗失文明?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.81,0:13:34.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,应该是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.41,0:13:35.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薄荷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.11,0:13:38.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，我立刻准备进行分析
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.25,0:13:39.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜托你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.28,0:13:42.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香草，能请你来帮忙一下吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.66,0:13:51.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，薄荷，请等一下我也要帮忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.73,0:14:00.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,马上就好了请稍微忍耐一下喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.33,0:14:03.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对了，你要不要看杂志或是什么的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.50,0:14:04.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅尔优
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.74,0:14:07.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里又不是美容院
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.74,0:14:09.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.51,0:14:10.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是不可思议
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.88,0:14:13.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不晓得为什么这女孩的体内组织
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.19,0:14:18.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,与这个遗失文明紧紧地结合在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.90,0:14:23.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,意思是说这个女孩一辈子无法拿掉这些宝石吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.76,0:14:28.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若能查出这个遗失文明的成分和结构或许有办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.10,0:14:30.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.66,0:14:37.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,靠我们至今收集的资料也无法比对出这个遗失文明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.40,0:14:38.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.28,0:14:48.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样啊连你们也无能为力啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.45,0:14:51.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在正在比对托朗斯巴皇军过去的资料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.62,0:14:54.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,重新调查有无相同案例
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.76,0:14:58.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是现阶段若查不比那个宝石的由来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.26,0:15:02.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就无法得知它与异常气候有无关联
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.16,0:15:04.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很抱歉，帮不上忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.50,0:15:07.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，这不是你们的错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.10,0:15:08.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这．．．这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.81,0:15:13.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过，话说回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.41,0:15:15.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雨这样每天下个不停
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.80,0:15:17.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,洗的衣服都乾不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.85,0:15:19.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的很头痛喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.68,0:15:21.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果只是下雨还好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.82,0:15:25.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地域纷争民族和宗教的对立
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.59,0:15:28.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有因此造成的极度贫困
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.53,0:15:36.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这几十年来都兰未曾停止过战争
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.13,0:15:40.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很多人死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.20,0:15:43.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很多人离开都兰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.47,0:15:51.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大概就在这场雨开始下了一年左右
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.45,0:15:55.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为雨的影响许多纠纷战争也都停战了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.88,0:16:02.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是却有更多人离开了这个逐渐沉入水中的都兰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.39,0:16:06.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如今留在这个星球上的只有贫困的人们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.93,0:16:09.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以及一小撮的伪善者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.43,0:16:13.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家一定都很疲惫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.11,0:16:24.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要不要一起喝杯茶?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.61,0:16:28.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像这样把热水注入茶壶里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.92,0:16:30.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後再把它闷一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.19,0:16:35.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样茶包也能泡出不输一般茶叶泡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.59,0:16:37.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好喝的红茶喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.16,0:16:44.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你讨厌喝红茶吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.17,0:16:49.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.67,0:16:55.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我其实很想把黏在你身上的遗失文明拿下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.28,0:17:00.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是现在的我只能泡红茶给你喝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.85,0:17:06.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里也．．．下雨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.55,0:17:09.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那不是下雨啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.16,0:17:13.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过，这个地方的确走到哪里都在下雨喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.16,0:17:15.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.73,0:17:19.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我现在想到了一件很棒的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.40,0:17:22.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出了什么事吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.54,0:17:26.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,教授，事情不妙了少女失踪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.17,0:17:27.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你说什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.31,0:17:29.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨蛋!说失踪了就没事吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.94,0:17:31.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还不快点去找
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.71,0:17:32.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.52,0:17:36.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我真是太聪明了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.38,0:17:39.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,开著纹章机就能到没有下雨的上空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.32,0:17:41.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来一场空中散步了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.86,0:17:45.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,偶尔还是要离开房间到外面走一走比较好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.46,0:17:48.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不然人会变得笨笨的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.13,0:17:55.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佛特，不得了了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.80,0:18:00.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅尔优带著那个女孩不晓得飞到哪里去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.47,0:18:01.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这下怎么办?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.78,0:18:02.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你说什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.94,0:18:05.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原来是你们夥伴干的好事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.11,0:18:08.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,紧急联络空军，立刻出动攻击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.38,0:18:09.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.88,0:18:11.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂，怎么突然要攻击?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.39,0:18:13.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要遗失文明在她身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.45,0:18:15.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个少女就是政府的最高机密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.61,0:18:18.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,结果你们的夥伴居然把她强行夺走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.64,0:18:20.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们不能放著不管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.96,0:18:24.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看样子现在跟他说什么都没有用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.90,0:18:25.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兰花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.90,0:18:26.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.73,0:18:28.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们也出动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.20,0:18:32.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么样?喜不喜欢空中散步呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.64,0:18:35.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,马上就能到云层上面去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.61,0:18:40.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里也在下雨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.48,0:18:42.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你刚才说什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.22,0:18:48.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,立刻回头，乖乖的回头进入我们的监视范围内
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.61,0:18:52.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你被怀疑有强行夺走遗失文明的嫌疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.66,0:18:54.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,立刻掉头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.26,0:18:56.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么强行夺走?这样太过份了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.43,0:18:59.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们只是在空中散步而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.14,0:19:03.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若不听从警告的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.58,0:19:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香草，有什么不对劲吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.75,0:19:16.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.68,0:19:19.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那女孩和这个星球的波长感应相互呼应著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.65,0:19:20.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.85,0:19:22.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你早就知道了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.56,0:19:24.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就请他们马上停止攻击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.93,0:19:28.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,失去那名少女的话这场雨的原因也．．．
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.76,0:19:31.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,教授，难道你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.67,0:19:32.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那女孩如果死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.73,0:19:36.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她与都兰的意识结合会消灭雨就会停
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.50,0:19:39.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个可能性是很高没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.81,0:19:42.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你该不会是认真的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.51,0:19:45.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们真的很累了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.98,0:19:51.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要能让这场雨停用任何手段都无所谓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.69,0:20:00.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们好像逃过一劫了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.49,0:20:02.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不要紧吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.10,0:20:05.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇怪?她到哪里去了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.88,0:20:19.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了，你平安无事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.85,0:20:21.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在看这朵花吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.82,0:20:26.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真可怜一定是我们迫降时扫到它的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.55,0:20:28.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像做了坏事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.62,0:20:31.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过，看它这个样子应该不要紧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.96,0:20:33.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,花的生命力可是很强的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.49,0:20:37.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算受了点伤只要让它晒晒阳光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.73,0:20:40.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又会精神奕奕的绽放
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.30,0:20:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对了，带这朵花去阳光照得到的地方吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.77,0:20:47.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样它一定能恢复元气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.51,0:20:54.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，没问题，可以飞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.28,0:20:56.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幸运星，出动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.97,0:21:22.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看，云层的上方永远都是阳光普照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.18,0:21:24.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然预定的散步有了一点改变
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.91,0:21:27.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过，为了这朵花也是没办法的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.28,0:21:32.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然晒了太阳也不会马上恢复元气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.39,0:21:34.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是只要慢慢的花时间照顾它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.60,0:21:37.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定会开得很漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.95,0:21:39.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就像用茶包泡红茶一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.14,0:22:26.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,学长，我喜欢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:26.67,0:22:29.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦，这样啊其实我也对你有好感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.88,0:22:31.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这种事怎样都好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:31.58,0:22:34.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我喜欢学长所以我要变成跟踪狂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.86,0:22:37.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你听我说，我也喜欢你所以没有必要变成跟踪狂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.15,0:22:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我没有办法压抑我的感情你会觉得很困扰吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.15,0:22:41.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟踪狂当然很困扰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.42,0:22:43.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要跟踪了我们好好交往不就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.12,0:22:44.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你果然还是不喜欢我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:44.36,0:22:46.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我明白了，我死心了，再见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.23,0:22:47.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦，再见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:48.66,0:22:49.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,启动认真模式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.60,0:22:50.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道该怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.36,0:22:52.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,超very紧张
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.63,0:22:54.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心儿呯呯跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.13,0:22:57.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,私奔极限
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.10,0:22:59.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,秘密进入
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:59.81,0:23:04.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宛如软绵绵的蛋白霜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:04.95,0:23:07.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心跳加速
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.38,0:23:09.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,冰淇淋派
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:09.82,0:23:11.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吻了你的心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.75,0:23:15.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快要溢出来的Jelly Beans
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:16.61,0:23:22.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拥抱五彩缤纷的心情
